Note: Date/Time Testing

Let now be the current date and time.
Say "Current Date/Time: " plus now.

Let y be the current year.
Say "Current Year: " plus y.

Let ts be the current timestamp.
Say "Current Timestamp: " plus ts.

Note: Throwing Errors Testing

Try the following.
    Say "Attempting to throw an error...".
    Throw error "This is a custom error!".
    Say "This should not print.".
Handle error and save it as err.
    Say "Caught an error: " plus err.
End try.
